                          "id": "d5fc8013-1c24-46c6-8726-b70813ef6bd8",
                          "text": {
                            "ops": [
                              {
                                "insert": "Without web search here, I cannot fully rule out that some sentences were lightly adapted from a specific blog, newsletter, or coach, but there is no evidence or citation in your context to attribute it to one."
                              },
