                          "id": "b227a0ee-6512-4f44-b09f-56bff37beb68",
                          "text": {
                            "ops": [
                              {
                                "insert": "If you intended a specific sentence in that block as “the claim” (e.g., about diet variety or decision fatigue) and want external empirical backing for "
                              },
                              {
                                "insert": "that",
                                "attributes": {
                                  "italic": true
                                }
                              },
                              {
                                "insert": " sentence, I would need you to highlight it so I can look specifically for primary research on that narrower point."
                              },
