    {
      "id": "VDqrmZERJKTFCxGj",
      "data": {
        "root": {
          "type": "root",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "cbf3d0e3-e228-4f3e-bc2e-bdd94cba7de9",
              "text": {
                "ops": [
                  {
                    "insert": "Weekly Priorities"
                  },
                  {
                    "insert": "\n",
                    "attributes": {
                      "paragraph": true
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              "format": null,
              "collapsed": false,
              "completed": false,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "15c508b7-bdce-4ee0-b6c7-9442c23deb3c",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "THE ONE THING"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "440f7603-478b-41a0-bfba-25ada2caf4f0",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "Fulfill the 400-unit Leger Boutique wholesale order on time this week."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "3fed7d24-ec16-4b87-9c46-bc09a4b0d1c1",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "b1b4e330-086f-4cb7-b27e-e9f8483f8b52",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "WHY THIS WEEK"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "34588235-8b32-48d4-8461-0701dbf6f6ac",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "The ship-by date is Friday 2026-04-17 per the signed PO. Leger's spring window resets Monday the 20th — miss the window and the full order gets rejected. The order is $18K, roughly 35% of Q2 forecast, and Leger is our first real department-store channel. A clean first fulfillment unlocks reorder conversations. A missed one kills the relationship with their buyer, who has already flagged us as \"unproven.\""
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "72640688-1102-44c8-a2eb-2dee3f21f9b2",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "f1300b54-b94f-4a01-bf71-4b40ee80b08f",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "WHAT WE'RE NOT DOING"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "d26dec5f-fb47-4661-afa4-9a733fef9b7d",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "1. Spring collection reveal (Marigold, Ink & Pine) — was scheduled to announce Thursday. Push to Tuesday 2026-04-21. Reason: Leger is a confirmed bird in hand; a collection launch is probabilistic. Newsletter tease still goes out, but no press outreach and no paid Instagram."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "99a4439f-d2ca-4a35-815f-3744b1a1ead9",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "2. Website product photography reshoot — supposed to happen Wednesday. Push two weeks. Reason: no orders depend on it, current photos are serviceable, the photographer has flexible rescheduling."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "42b0f02c-223f-4efb-bc1a-fcf7ae6f00ea",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "3. Responding to Mei's ingredient-sourcing partnership offer — needs a thoughtful reply, not a rushed one. Reason: we would be committing to a supply chain decision under pressure, which is when we make bad ones."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "fec365ed-4237-444b-bc39-e5b27ff072f6",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "a0ca383d-7a35-4948-adce-bf70731ddafa",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "THE TRADEOFF"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "d8652bf5-86ed-4cd2-bfee-c1dce37421b5",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "We trade creative momentum for operational discipline. The spring collection has been in our heads for three months and we have been promising the newsletter a reveal. Holding it costs real goodwill with subscribers and a small amount of Instagram reach during the week everyone else is launching."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "2db90a14-217b-491e-ae57-c29f93b3ded0",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "e160d5fa-c84b-45ea-97e4-659071b976fb",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "The emotional cost is higher than the PR cost. Stopping something you are excited to ship and redirecting to bottling and labeling is demoralizing work. Budget for this explicitly — take Wednesday afternoon off if we hit our midweek milestone, and do not squeeze both projects into the same week on adrenaline. The collection launches either way; it launches 11 days later with a rested team or this Thursday with a cracked one."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "d277a1fa-6d5d-422b-a9d1-1aac153a9fbd",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "900c199c-74ec-4f79-853a-92a9f2fb47c3",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "THE SIGNAL TO WATCH"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "4cd582a1-92ee-4cbc-bb2e-fe32bf0b09a8",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "Units completed by end of day Wednesday. Target is 250 by Wed EOD — 80 units/day Mon, Tue, Wed, with Thursday for QC and Friday morning for packaging and shipping. If we are under 200 by Wed EOD, we cannot hit 400 by Friday without a weekend push, and a weekend push will burn us out before the collection launch the following week."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "748b5eef-2a3b-4b17-835f-39a47ebcb9e6",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "101e995c-2323-47f5-8807-848f7b45959b",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "Secondary signal: cap-seal QC failure rate. If more than 3% of units fail first-pass inspection, the bottleneck is the sealer, not the labor. Pull the backup sealer from storage Tuesday morning before it becomes the Thursday emergency."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "28672b39-90b3-4e9e-97ce-e469bfa3f29d",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "d6dfe283-bdc9-4e32-9aeb-c4ed8ff05467",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "RISK"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "eb1d4504-1d6d-4f95-b0c1-944688fe4a51",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "What could invalidate this by Friday:"
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "8fda8cac-4de5-434e-8f78-e60a528f8b1d",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- Clary sage shipment late. Bloomsbury Supply was supposed to deliver Monday morning and it has not arrived. Without it we can only make 280 of the 400 — the Marigold batch needs clary sage. Mitigation: call Bloomsbury by 10 AM. If they cannot confirm Tuesday arrival, substitute the bergamot-forward variant and notify Leger's buyer directly before we switch. Never switch silently."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "5922cd14-4d8a-4ecb-a407-571384f7f07e",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- Second dryer fails again. It has failed twice in March. Replacement is $4,200 and backordered 8 days. Mitigation: if it fails, shift to the cedar drying racks — adds 18 hours per batch but does not kill the timeline. Do not attempt to repair in-house a third time; we are not electricians."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "da0aaa30-9253-4c56-9eb4-97084a790c68",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "- Leger's buyer pulls the ship date forward to Thursday. She mentioned last week it \"might happen.\" Mitigation: confirm the ship date in writing by EOD today. If she pulls it, we drop to 320 units, ship partial, and get her written agreement on the partial BEFORE we commit."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "1e1dd483-f4a7-438a-ac2a-d66a322b6902",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "5b7e2854-b9cb-44f1-9f69-2cb804863d7d",
                  "text": {
                    "ops": [
                      {
                        "insert": "If any of these fires hard, fall back to shipping 280 units of the core order — everything except Marigold — take the partial-fulfillment hit, and preserve the relationship. That is ~$12K of $18K and keeps Leger on the hook for the reorder conversation. Do not ship 400 units of substandard product to hit the number; a quality failure ends the relationship faster than a partial one."
                      },
                      {
                        "insert": "\n",
                        "attributes": {
                          "paragraph": true
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "format": {
                    "node": "text",
                    "children": "text"
                  },
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "completed": false,
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
